1
00:00:03,640 --> 00:00:04,600
(Qibo Medical Centre)

2
00:00:04,720 --> 00:00:05,520
Mr Liu,

3
00:00:05,720 --> 00:00:07,757
it is normal and very positive

4
00:00:07,840 --> 00:00:09,477
for young people to pursue their dreams.

5
00:00:09,560 --> 00:00:11,000
But if you want to hide

6
00:00:11,120 --> 00:00:13,157
and obtain this certificate
just because of that,

7
00:00:13,240 --> 00:00:14,360
I don't think it's worth it.

8
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:15,360
Look at

9
00:00:15,480 --> 00:00:17,000
how hard he's practising dancing now,

10
00:00:17,280 --> 00:00:19,557
there's a good chance he will win
awards, and even become a champion.

11
00:00:19,640 --> 00:00:21,160
Once this kind of thing is uncovered,

12
00:00:22,040 --> 00:00:23,317
so many eyes will be on him,

13
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:24,200
criticizing him.

14
00:00:24,640 --> 00:00:25,877
It will be too late to regret it then.

15
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:28,280
You know what will happen?
It will ruin his public image.

16
00:00:28,560 --> 00:00:29,360
It's very serious.

17
00:00:29,520 --> 00:00:30,320
Liu,

18
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:33,197
Tou Tou made a very good point.

19
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:34,080
Tou Tou,

20
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:36,200
I'm really impressed.

21
00:00:36,400 --> 00:00:37,640
Liu, sit down.

22
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:41,440
Let's do what Tou Tou said, okay?

23
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:45,080
I know you have helped me a lot.

24
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:47,640
I will find another way to repay you,

25
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:49,997
but I can't do

26
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:51,440
what you asked of me today.

27
00:00:52,120 --> 00:00:54,320
Because this concerns
your child's entire life.

28
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:57,160
We need to proceed with caution.

29
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:58,320
Don't you think so?

30
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:01,600
You are right, Professor.

31
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:02,760
I will listen to you.

32
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:04,720
What about me?

33
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,320
I said a lot just now.

34
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,440
I...

35
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,680
You were right too.

36
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,240
Let's be clear.

37
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:12,037
You chose this path,

38
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,720
so you'd better see it through the end.

39
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:16,520
Don't worry about it, Dad.

40
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:21,237
Well, I guess it's settled then.

41
00:01:21,320 --> 00:01:24,160
I heard that Ms Dong is practising
in your clinic.

42
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:27,600
You know that I have issues
with my neck and lumbar spine.

43
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:29,717
Could you please introduce me to her?

44
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:31,440
It's my duty to help.

45
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,280
-Okay.
-I'll take you there right now.

46
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:35,000
-Thank you.
-All right.

47
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:38,797
He's really worrying.

48
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:40,080
Yes, yes,

49
00:01:41,440 --> 00:01:43,040
but we can't just leave him be.

50
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:53,000
You're wearing so many clothes.

51
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,600
Aren't you feeling uncomfortably hot?

52
00:01:58,320 --> 00:02:00,080
-So old-fashioned.
-What did you say?

53
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,640
Little brat.

54
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,680
You are so smug.

55
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:01,120
Help!

56
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:02,840
Help!

57
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:06,040
Help!

58
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,200
Anyone there?

59
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,360
What's wrong?

60
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:11,560
What's wrong?

61
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,560
My baby...

62
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,757
-Your water broke.
-My baby...

63
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,800
You're going into labour.

64
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,957
Hold on. You need to relax.
Come, come.

65
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:21,280
Stretch your legs out. Relax.

66
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:22,757
Listen to me, do as I say.

67
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:23,920
I'm here. You will be fine.

68
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:25,160
It's you!

69
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:26,920
Oh, my God!

70
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:32,557
I can't believe I would even run
into a jinx like you in the cemetery.

71
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:33,760
Don't touch me!

72
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,440
(Qibo Medical Centre)

73
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:42,520
When I ignored you,

74
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,520
you flourished.

75
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:48,600
Now that I'm taking such
meticulous care of you every day.

76
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,200
Yet how did you end up
looking like this?

77
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:53,760
Did you see my phone?

78
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,800
-Pardon me?
-My phone?

79
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,480
I didn't see it.

80
00:04:01,440 --> 00:04:02,320
Master.

81
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:04,400
What's the matter?

82
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,600
Jian Xi is here.

83
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:10,720
Cursing me now won't help you, you know?

84
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:12,317
Your baby is
the most important thing now.

85
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,797
You hear me? It's your baby.

86
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:15,000
Trust me.

87
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,480
I'm a doctor.

88
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:17,800
Straighten your legs.

89
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:18,840
Oh, God.

90
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:21,120
I'm not going to die here, am I?

91
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:24,400
You won't die. You're just giving birth.

92
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,760
Our whole family

93
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:28,397
is going to die in your hands.

94
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,680
-Come.
-No...

95
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:30,877
You mustn't get agitated.

96
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,920
You have to conserve your strength,
you hear me?

97
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,437
You have to conserve your strength
to push, okay?

98
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:37,717
I'm calling an ambulance
for you now, okay?

99
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,320
Hang in there, you hear me?

100
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,080
No.

101
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:45,160
Even if you call an ambulance,

102
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:47,160
we're deep in the mountains,

103
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:50,720
by the time the ambulance arrives,
I'll be dead already.

104
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,440
Touch wood. You won't die.

105
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,040
Hang in there.

106
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:56,237
Hello? Hello?

107
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,840
Hello? Is this the first aid centre?

108
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,640
I'm at Mushan Cemetery.

109
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:02,200
I'm on a path.

110
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:05,240
A woman is going into labour here.

111
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,597
Can you guys come now?

112
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:07,480
Don't leave.

113
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:09,277
Don't go. Save my baby.

114
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:11,437
-I'm not leaving, I'm not leaving.
-Save my baby!

115
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:13,077
Hold on. I need to find a landmark.

116
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,800
Hello? There is no landmark here.

117
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:15,837
Can you come right now?

118
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,040
It's an emergency.

119
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,360
Okay, okay.

120
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,000
What's wrong?

121
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,400
I'm feeling...

122
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,240
I'm feeling...

123
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,480
I'm feeling that he's coming out.

124
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:28,720
Hang on.

125
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,400
He's coming out.

126
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,077
Here. Sit here.

127
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:33,957
Relax.

128
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:34,840
Take a deep breath.

129
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:35,880
Take a deep breath.

130
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,040
Don't worry. I'm here.

131
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,797
Chen Hui, hang in there. Chen Hui!

132
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:40,920
I can't.

133
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:42,880
I'm here. Don't worry.

134
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:52,400
(Qibo Medical Centre)

135
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:53,920
Jian Xi,

136
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,480
why have you lost so much weight?

137
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,840
Didn't she take the medicine
prescribed last time?

138
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:00,880
She did.

139
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,160
It has no effect at all.

140
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,677
Now she eats even less.

141
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:05,597
Lately, she won't even
take a bite of food.

142
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:08,080
Could her injury have caused
some other illness?

143
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:19,600
How about this? You guys go out first.

144
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,960
I'd like a moment alone with Jian Xi.

145
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,800
Professor Ren,

146
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,440
what's wrong with Jian Xi?

147
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,000
Is it serious?

148
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,240
I think

149
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:31,600
she's fine.

150
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,680
How can she be fine?

151
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:34,920
She won't even

152
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:37,120
eat now.

153
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,717
Just tell me the truth.

154
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,800
I can handle it.

155
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,400
You need to trust Professor Ren.

156
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,200
If he says it's nothing serious,

157
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,880
then there shouldn't be any problem.

158
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,080
Let's step outside for a moment, okay?

159
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,280
Plus,

160
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,600
Jian Xi will feel nervous

161
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,640
with you here.

162
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:57,560
Come.

163
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,040
Come.

164
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,520
Let me read your pulse.

165
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:29,477
Mr Ren. Mr Ren.

166
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,200
Please pick up the phone, Mr Ren!

167
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:33,760
Oh, no.

168
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,560
My battery is running out.

169
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:38,560
Chen Hui, where is your phone?
Give me your phone.

170
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,800
Forget about me.

171
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,720
Tear it open for me.

172
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,400
Protect my baby.

173
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,280
Tear it open for me.

174
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:47,760
The ambulance... When will

175
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:50,120
the ambulance arrive?

176
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,800
-When?
-An hour.

177
00:07:52,193 --> 00:07:53,310
No, no, 40 minutes.

178
00:07:53,394 --> 00:07:55,028
-An hour?
-40 minutes.

179
00:07:55,112 --> 00:07:56,237
-40 minutes?
-Yes, yes.

180
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:58,237
I've also called
the village doctor here.

181
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:00,477
It's okay. He'll be here soon.
Hang in there.

182
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:02,357
I'll be dead already.

183
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,440
You won't.

184
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,840
My baby will also be dead already.

185
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:08,840
We will both die here.

186
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:10,835
Mr Ren.

187
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,108
No.

188
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,440
I have to go see him.

189
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,160
Tear it open for me.

190
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:17,640
Take my baby out.

191
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,760
Save him.

192
00:08:19,739 --> 00:08:20,979
If it's a boy,

193
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,676
name him...

194
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,400
Name him Kong Nian Yuan.

195
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:27,880
If it's a girl, name her Kong Ai Yuan.

196
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,760
-Can you remember it?
-Okay, okay. I got it.

197
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,080
-Can you remember it?
-I got it.

198
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:32,720
You will be fine, Chen Hui.

199
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,280
Hang in there!

200
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:37,080
Chen Hui, hang in there!
Don't...

201
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,560
When will the ambulance get here?

202
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,120
You killed my husband.

203
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,280
Why...

204
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:55,560
Why didn't you save him?

205
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:57,400
(You must cherish)

206
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:59,917
(your time here.)

207
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,680
Don't wait until you encounter patients

208
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:03,560
or unexpected events

209
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:04,840
and find yourself helpless,

210
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:06,440
only then you regret for

211
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:08,357
not having learned

212
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:10,520
a useful skill here.

213
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:13,117
I'm the devil. Look at me, Chen Hui.

214
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,117
I'm the devil.

215
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,560
So, you have to hang in there.

216
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,437
You haven't settled
the score with me yet.

217
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,997
You have to come after me, you know?

218
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:20,157
You have to stay alive.

219
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,680
Do you hear me, Chen Hui?

220
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,357
-Chen Hui?
-Help me.

221
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,520
I'll help you, I will.

222
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:26,640
Stay with me, Chen Hui.

223
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,760
Chen Hui, hang in there! Chen Hui!

224
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:45,080
Your pulse is weak,

225
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,360
but it isn't a big issue.

226
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,320
Be honest with me,

227
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:53,760
have you

228
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:55,560
stopped eating?

229
00:09:57,920 --> 00:10:00,360
There is no such thing as using tiles
as medicine, is there?

230
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:04,560
I'll never be able to walk again,

231
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,400
will I?

232
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,480
You've been lying to me,

233
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,520
haven't you?

234
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:54,320
Chen Hui.

235
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,880
Chen Hui, listen to me,

236
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:58,440
the ambulance is on its way,

237
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:00,200
but we can't wait anymore.

238
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:02,197
I will help you deliver, okay?

239
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:03,637
Just do as I say.

240
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,677
We will push together.

241
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:06,040
You and your baby will be fine,

242
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:07,240
okay? Trust me.

243
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:09,200
Save my baby.

244
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:16,080
My baby...

245
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:37,520
Your baby is in an incorrect position.

246
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:39,760
He is not head-down.

247
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:42,520
What should I do?

248
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:47,237
Save my baby first.

249
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,077
You have to save my baby first.

250
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:50,477
I... I'm going

251
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,917
to reach in now

252
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,440
and try to...

253
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:55,120
Try to turn the baby's head downward.

254
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:57,600
He will be fine. He will be fine, okay?

255
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,560
Trust me. He will be fine.

256
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:14,400
Hang in there.
I'm about to reach the baby's head.

257
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:21,560
I reached it.

258
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:24,277
Hang in there, Chen Hui.

259
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,160
Hang in there.

260
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,200
Can you feel my hand?

261
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:32,240
-Yes.
-Relax now.

262
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:36,480
Okay. It's okay now.

263
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:38,680
Chen Hui,

264
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,357
now listen to my instructions.

265
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,397
I will count to three,

266
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:42,320
and then you push.

267
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:43,880
Push with all your strength.

268
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,600
Come on. One, two, three.

269
00:12:46,560 --> 00:12:47,400
Push!

270
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,440
Okay. Try again.

271
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:58,320
Can you push again?

272
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:00,120
I can't.

273
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,077
I can't push anymore.

274
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:02,597
-You can do it, Chen Hui.
-I can't.

275
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:04,720
You can do it, Chen Hui.
We are almost there.

276
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:06,280
You have to hang in there, Chen Hui.

277
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:08,560
Let's try to push again, okay?

278
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:09,560
Let's try it again.

279
00:13:09,880 --> 00:13:12,437
One, two, three!

280
00:13:12,520 --> 00:13:13,520
Push!

281
