643
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:30,040
so you see no dust.

644
00:30:30,800 --> 00:30:31,800
I can't do it.

645
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:33,920
I don't have your
level of enlightenment.

646
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:35,080
You can put on socks

647
