697
00:33:42,320 --> 00:33:44,160
Integrity is what the way
of nature requires.

698
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:46,357
Acting with integrity is the way
to achieve self-refinement.

699
00:33:46,440 --> 00:33:47,680
Weren't these your words?

700
00:33:48,520 --> 00:33:49,477
One should not lie,

701
00:33:49,560 --> 00:33:51,200
