711
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:29,000
The most important thing for a doctor

712
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:31,360
is compassion.

713
00:34:33,900 --> 00:34:34,876
(Compassion)

714
00:34:34,960 --> 00:34:36,440
Heaven has the virtue of nurturing life.

715
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:38,320
I believe that the ancient sages

716
00:34:38,513 --> 00:34:41,073
would not punish me

717
00:34:41,427 --> 00:34:43,547
for wholeheartedly
attending to my patients.

718
00:34:44,720 --> 00:34:46,880
If there were truly
any punishments for me,

719
00:34:48,040 --> 00:34:49,040
as long as it means that

720
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:51,000
Jian Xi,

721
00:34:51,720 --> 00:34:52,517
her mother,

722
00:34:52,600 --> 00:34:53,557
and Cheng Ying

723
00:34:53,640 --> 00:34:54,720
can escape this calamity,

724
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:55,800
