not pursue that path.

774
00:37:21,560 --> 00:37:24,640
Technology is advancing
rapidly these days.

775
00:37:25,280 --> 00:37:26,800
Who knows, in another year

776
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:28,240
or two,

777
00:37:31,280 --> 00:37:32,560
